@node "CREDITS" "Program credits and greets!!"
                              Project Credits
                              ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    This entire project was written using AMOSPro, and uses no external
extensions other than those supplied with the package. It took 4 days to
complete the demo version, with a further 3 days adding pieces and changing
routines for the fully registered version. All programming was done by
Andrew "Mushroom" Kellett using an A1200, with 2Mb chip, 4Mb FAST, Blizzard
1220 and FPU, 14.4K modem, 200Mb HD and external floppy drive.

